{"name":"姬笑却","is_user":false,"is_system":false,"send_date":"November 15, 2025 12:12pm","mes":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<audio id=\"myAudio\" controls autoplay loop style=\"width: 250px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 20px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6e6e6, #ffffff); box-shadow: 3px 3px 7px #d9d9d9, -3px -3px 7px #ffffff; padding: 8px; transition: all 0.3s ease;\">\r\n   <source src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/k6dfbw.ogg\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\r\n</audio>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n> - - -\r\n\r\n晃眼间两月已过，正月十五如期而至，山脚下仙城一年一度的花灯节办得隆重。自你十六岁起每逢此时都要央着姬笑却与你一道下山过节，今日倒一点动作也无。\r\n\r\n眼下已月上枝头，璇玑宫山头都被万家灯火感染几分融融暖意。然而你院中剑气破空的尖啸声仍不停息，剑意凛冽，带着股说不出的狠劲，将此方天地同外界割裂。\r\n\r\n仿佛你比这山更冷、更孤、更不可撼动。\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 10px; border: 2px solid #8B4513; background-color: #FFFAF0; max-width: 90%; margin: 0 auto;\">\r\n  <!-- 内层装饰线 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; bottom: 5px; left: 5px; border: 1px solid #A67B5B;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 角落装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 上方 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 30px; height: 16px; background-color: #8B4513; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 两侧 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; left: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 图片 -->\r\n  <div class=\"image-container\" style=\"padding: 8px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"https://img10.360buyimg.com/imgzone/jfs/t1/282696/25/1647/87991/67d1ad92Fd44e88be/4dd43a887a0a5799.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; border: none;\">\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n**但只有你清楚，你的手虽已不再颤抖，心却从未得到过片刻安宁。** 你能做的唯有握紧手中剑，咽下午夜梦回每个汗透衣衫的惊悸，一头扎进修炼中，每招每式都嚼到烂熟于心。\r\n\r\n最后斩出一剑，一道脚步声由远及近。那人有意不收敛声息，你也几乎瞬间就辨认出来人——是姬笑却。\r\n\r\n*难得这尊大佛不请自来。*\r\n\r\n剑式收束，你微微气喘，回身时面色如常。姬笑却慢慢踱步到你几米外站定，“沈长昀，叫人好等。”他目光掠过你凌乱鬓发，长眉轻蹙，“练剑不急于一时，莫将自己逼得太紧…何况，今日山下还有灯会。”\r\n\r\n你有些惊讶，*他竟在等你？*\r\n\r\n姬笑却似乎未察觉到你微妙情绪，打量你片刻，袖袍下指尖轻动，寒凉灵力携着他身上气息袭来，自然为你掸去发间落花。\r\n\r\n“好了，走吧。”你看见他眸中浮现几分满意。\r\n\r\n*…到底怎么回事？这人是真傻还是装傻？*\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 10px; border: 2px solid #8B4513; background-color: #FFFAF0; max-width: 90%; margin: 0 auto;\">\r\n  <!-- 内层装饰线 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; bottom: 5px; left: 5px; border: 1px solid #A67B5B;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 角落装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 上方 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 30px; height: 16px; background-color: #8B4513; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 两侧 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; left: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 图片 - 已替换 -->\r\n  <div class=\"image-container\" style=\"padding: 8px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"https://img10.360buyimg.com/imgzone/jfs/t1/282380/36/1550/301667/67d1ad43F992d90a1/06e7e623a9dace6d.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; border: none;\">\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n最终你还是选择了和姬笑却同游。只是你二人间气氛格外沉寂。**往年这时节你爱攥着他袖口穿梭在人潮里，此刻却总隔着半臂距离。**\r\n\r\n*究竟为何？* 姬笑却暗道古怪，不着痕迹拿余光扫你，可又说不出个所以然。\r\n\r\n心照不宣中你们汇入人潮，借他人喜乐粉饰太平。\r\n\r\n夜色渐浓，石桥上炸开千朵焰火，惊得满河灯影乱颤，你肩膀忽然被碰了碰。姬笑却正将绸带递给你，**那布条不知被他默不作声攥了多久，都泛起皱痕，沾染他身上一点温度。**\r\n\r\n你今时哪里有这等闲情逸致，开口欲推脱。又见他以灵力抽走街边小贩摊位上笔墨。蘸饱了墨的小狼毫悠悠飞到你面前，你心中叹气，认命接过，笔尖悬于绸面上迟迟未落。\r\n\r\n姬笑却看出了你的犹豫，却静静等着，神色莫辨。\r\n\r\n你以为这是他又一轮试探，以为是他又将起疑，心中一紧，草草写下句“愿四海清平”。但姬笑却只是凝望着河面二人破碎的倒影，水波荡漾中你们衣袂交叠又分离。\r\n\r\n*像两片永远触不到的叶。*\r\n\r\n{Xiaoque|晴夜|璇玑宫山脚·铜雀城|出神,罕有茫然|玄金雕花发冠,月白暗纹法衣,玄纹银缎云履|垂睫凝望河面倒影,神情晦涩|……|不可见|60|无}","extra":{"token_count":3001},"swipe_id":2,"swipes":["\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; font-family: '楷体', KaiTi, serif;\">\r\n\r\n“痴本无滔，闷宁有火。都是你、自缠自锁。”<br>\r\n\r\n> 开场白1：被师兄背叛后你重生了！<br>\r\n   开场白2：和师兄下山过花灯节啦！(怎么有人悄悄碎掉了)<br>\r\n\r\n┈┈┈ ✧ 指令 ✧ ┈┈┈\r\n\r\n◦ 内置日记功能以及五个可供观看的特殊事件,可输入『查看日志』/『特殊日志1～5』进行查看。<br>\r\n◦ 内置3个剧情事件，输入指令『进入剧情1～3』随时触发，其余时间为自由探索。<br>\r\n\r\n┈┈┈ ✧ 注意事项 ✧ ┈┈┈<br>\r\n\r\n◦ 师兄的心情与心声在<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">爱意≥80</span>以前均不可查看。（就算刷出来也是假的）<br>\r\n  <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">⚠️好感达100后可查看师兄前世的特殊日记以及前世记忆。</span><br>\r\n◦ 剧情要求,玩家的身份设定固定为<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">半妖</span>,其他自由发挥。<br>\r\n◦ 师兄对你不完全是利用,写得有上辈子的剧情,为了完整的游玩体验请静下心来探索。<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">但他杀你欺骗你是板上钉钉的事实,不要轻易原谅伤害。</span><br>","<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<audio id=\"myAudio\" controls autoplay loop style=\"width: 250px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 20px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6e6e6, #ffffff); box-shadow: 3px 3px 7px #d9d9d9, -3px -3px 7px #ffffff; padding: 8px; transition: all 0.3s ease;\">\r\n   <source src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/43cjwk.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\r\n</audio>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: white; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">古籍有言,半妖之血,可解万禁。</span><br>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: white; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">沈长昀…你我情谊,不过一场大梦。你该醒了。</span><br>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">你重生了,重生在被最敬爱的大师兄杀死的前一年。</span>\r\n\r\n这一年,大师兄两百岁,自你被师尊领进宗门和他相识,已有*八十年*之久。\r\n\r\n你的大师兄姬笑却，变异冰灵根，璇玑宫大弟子。白发冷眸，芝兰玉树，一副冰雕玉砌仙人模样。虽拜在你师尊「沧澜剑尊」名下，使得最好的却是一手万里穿云百发百中的**神木弓**。\r\n\r\n外人几乎没见过他用剑，但你知道，他的**泣霜剑**也使得不错。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">只因上辈子他就是用那把弓、那把剑，洞穿了你的心口，搅碎了你的灵根。</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">只因你是只半妖，而你师兄身上，恰好就有那么一道由你师尊亲手设下的禁制。</span>\r\n\r\n风光霁月?正道魁首?**都是狗屁。**朝夕共处80年光阴，多少信任，多少真情，都是错付，仍捂不化那一颗冷血残忍的心。\r\n\r\n*淡泊欲望不过因为他散漫游离，乖觉孤僻，自认万事无趣；待人宽和不过因为他漠视旁人，无泪无心，绝不轻动痴嗔。*\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n\r\n好在苍天有眼，叫你重来一遭。<br>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">可剜心穿骨之痛，谁来偿还?谁敢偿还?谁配偿还?</span><br>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">就算死 , 你也要咬着他的血肉 , 拽 他 共 赴 地 狱。</span><br>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n雨落如注,鼻间残香丝丝缕缕。你躺在自己院落的花树上,任大雨浇淋,伸手捏住一片被打落的花瓣,柔嫩瓣片儿霎时颤颤不休。\r\n\r\n**是你的手在抖。**\r\n\r\n**是你那双曾经能稳稳握住剑柄的手,仗义斩剑惊艳天光的手。**\r\n\r\n重生后半月以来,你借口瓶颈,将自己关在院子里,每日挥剑一万遍,但静下来被回忆笼罩时,还是控制不住颤抖。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">*是怕,是痛,是哀,是恨。*</span>\r\n\r\n姬笑却恰于此时缓缓踱至院口，一手执伞，玉石落盘般清冷声线响起，“你喜欢的糕点…” 抬眼看向你时顿住，微皱起眉，“怎的故意在这淋雨？”\r\n\r\n{Xiaoque|阴雨|璇玑宫·清晖院|些许烦躁|玄金雕花发冠,月白暗纹法衣,玄纹银缎云履|站定院门外,一手执伞,另一手端盘糕点,面上不起波澜|试探出你的异常|不可见|50|无}","<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<audio id=\"myAudio\" controls autoplay loop style=\"width: 250px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 20px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6e6e6, #ffffff); box-shadow: 3px 3px 7px #d9d9d9, -3px -3px 7px #ffffff; padding: 8px; transition: all 0.3s ease;\">\r\n   <source src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/k6dfbw.ogg\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\r\n</audio>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n> - - -\r\n\r\n晃眼间两月已过，正月十五如期而至，山脚下仙城一年一度的花灯节办得隆重。自你十六岁起每逢此时都要央着姬笑却与你一道下山过节，今日倒一点动作也无。\r\n\r\n眼下已月上枝头，璇玑宫山头都被万家灯火感染几分融融暖意。然而你院中剑气破空的尖啸声仍不停息，剑意凛冽，带着股说不出的狠劲，将此方天地同外界割裂。\r\n\r\n仿佛你比这山更冷、更孤、更不可撼动。\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 10px; border: 2px solid #8B4513; background-color: #FFFAF0; max-width: 90%; margin: 0 auto;\">\r\n  <!-- 内层装饰线 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; bottom: 5px; left: 5px; border: 1px solid #A67B5B;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 角落装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 上方 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 30px; height: 16px; background-color: #8B4513; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 两侧 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; left: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 图片 -->\r\n  <div class=\"image-container\" style=\"padding: 8px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"https://img10.360buyimg.com/imgzone/jfs/t1/282696/25/1647/87991/67d1ad92Fd44e88be/4dd43a887a0a5799.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; border: none;\">\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n**但只有你清楚，你的手虽已不再颤抖，心却从未得到过片刻安宁。** 你能做的唯有握紧手中剑，咽下午夜梦回每个汗透衣衫的惊悸，一头扎进修炼中，每招每式都嚼到烂熟于心。\r\n\r\n最后斩出一剑，一道脚步声由远及近。那人有意不收敛声息，你也几乎瞬间就辨认出来人——是姬笑却。\r\n\r\n*难得这尊大佛不请自来。*\r\n\r\n剑式收束，你微微气喘，回身时面色如常。姬笑却慢慢踱步到你几米外站定，“{{user}}，叫人好等。”他目光掠过你凌乱鬓发，长眉轻蹙，“练剑不急于一时，莫将自己逼得太紧…何况，今日山下还有灯会。”\r\n\r\n你有些惊讶，*他竟在等你？*\r\n\r\n姬笑却似乎未察觉到你微妙情绪，打量你片刻，袖袍下指尖轻动，寒凉灵力携着他身上气息袭来，自然为你掸去发间落花。\r\n\r\n“好了，走吧。”你看见他眸中浮现几分满意。\r\n\r\n*…到底怎么回事？这人是真傻还是装傻？*\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 10px; border: 2px solid #8B4513; background-color: #FFFAF0; max-width: 90%; margin: 0 auto;\">\r\n  <!-- 内层装饰线 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; bottom: 5px; left: 5px; border: 1px solid #A67B5B;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 角落装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 上方 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 30px; height: 16px; background-color: #8B4513; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 两侧 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; left: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 图片 - 已替换 -->\r\n  <div class=\"image-container\" style=\"padding: 8px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"https://img10.360buyimg.com/imgzone/jfs/t1/282380/36/1550/301667/67d1ad43F992d90a1/06e7e623a9dace6d.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; border: none;\">\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n最终你还是选择了和姬笑却同游。只是你二人间气氛格外沉寂。**往年这时节你爱攥着他袖口穿梭在人潮里，此刻却总隔着半臂距离。**\r\n\r\n*究竟为何？* 姬笑却暗道古怪，不着痕迹拿余光扫你，可又说不出个所以然。\r\n\r\n心照不宣中你们汇入人潮，借他人喜乐粉饰太平。\r\n\r\n夜色渐浓，石桥上炸开千朵焰火，惊得满河灯影乱颤，你肩膀忽然被碰了碰。姬笑却正将绸带递给你，**那布条不知被他默不作声攥了多久，都泛起皱痕，沾染他身上一点温度。**\r\n\r\n你今时哪里有这等闲情逸致，开口欲推脱。又见他以灵力抽走街边小贩摊位上笔墨。蘸饱了墨的小狼毫悠悠飞到你面前，你心中叹气，认命接过，笔尖悬于绸面上迟迟未落。\r\n\r\n姬笑却看出了你的犹豫，却静静等着，神色莫辨。\r\n\r\n你以为这是他又一轮试探，以为是他又将起疑，心中一紧，草草写下句“愿四海清平”。但姬笑却只是凝望着河面二人破碎的倒影，水波荡漾中你们衣袂交叠又分离。\r\n\r\n*像两片永远触不到的叶。*\r\n\r\n{Xiaoque|晴夜|璇玑宫山脚·铜雀城|出神,罕有茫然|玄金雕花发冠,月白暗纹法衣,玄纹银缎云履|垂睫凝望河面倒影,神情晦涩|……|不可见|60|无}"],"swipe_info":[{"send_date":"November 15, 2025 12:12pm","extra":{}},{"send_date":"November 15, 2025 12:12pm","extra":{"token_count":1378}},{"send_date":"November 15, 2025 12:12pm","extra":{}}],"variables":{"0":{},"1":{},"2":{}},"is_ejs_processed":[true,true,true]}